ally shown to be good enough to\nobtain best possible regularized solutions for severely and moderately\nill-posed problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2015 02:29:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jul 2015 04:40:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2016 09:25:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-24"}
